<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩٥٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٌ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>. وَحَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5669">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ صَبَّاحٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/659">إِسْمَاعِيلُ بْنُ زَكَرِيَّاءَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«السَّمْعُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَالطَّاعَةُ حَقٌّ مَا لَمْ يُؤْمَرْ بِالْمَعْصِيَةِ فَإِذَا أُمِرَ بِمَعْصِيَةٍ فَلَا سَمْعَ وَلَا طَاعَةَ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>